00:24:49.624 --> 00:24:52.058
another woman:
"Long ago the older woman,

00:24:52.058 --> 00:24:54.506
the elder women,
would tell us that the only

00:24:54.506 --> 00:24:57.691
time you could sleep with
another man was if your husband

00:24:57.691 --> 00:24:59.910
was not able to make you
pregnant,

00:24:59.910 --> 00:25:03.848
but it's not that way
anymore."

00:25:03.848 --> 00:25:07.310
The moderator again asks,
"Once you got the baby of

00:25:07.310 --> 00:25:10.080
the other man,
was it for your husband or the

00:25:10.080 --> 00:25:11.338
other man?"
 

00:25:11.338 --> 00:25:14.346
Notice the for is taken for
granted that this is a gift,

00:25:14.346 --> 00:25:17.353
and who did you make the gift
for, is it a gift for your

00:25:17.353 --> 00:25:19.538
